<h4 id="tue-feb-1-computers-and-files-and-servers-oh-my">Tue., Feb. 1: Computers and Files and Servers, Oh My!</h4>
<ul>
  <li>Register for a personal account and domain name with <a href="https://reclaimhosting.com/shared-hosting/">Reclaim Hosting</a>
    <ul>
      <li>Cost: $30. This will be the only thing I will ask you to pay for during the semester (I hope).</li>
      <li>This URL will be your own personal domain that you will use in this class for assignments, but you can also use it moving forward as a professional website or portfolio. Think carefully about the domain name you choose - I would highly recommend using some version of your name - ie. <a href="https://cameronblevins.org">https://cameronblevins.org</a>.</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Annotate in Hypothesis:
